Package: mltools
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ben Gorman
Maintainer: Ben Gorman <bgorman@GormAnalysis.com>
Description: A collection of functions for machine learning including evaluation metrics, data binning methods, one-hot encoding, cross-validation fold generation, and tools for exploratory analysis. Makes heavy use of the 'data.table' package.
